quran[52]{c,v,t}:
  68,1,Nun. Pali cholembera ndi zimene amalemba
  68,2,"Mwachisomo cha Ambuye wako, sindiwe wamisala ayi"
  68,3,Ndithudi iwe udzalandira mphotho yosatha
  68,4,Ndithudi iwe uli ndi makhalidwe abwino
  68,5,Iwe udzaona ndipo nawo adzaona
  68,6,Kuti ndani wa inu amene ndi wamisala
  68,7,Ndithudi Ambuye wako amadziwa bwino amene wasochera ku njira yake ndipo amadziwa bwino amene amayenda m’njira yoyenera
  68,8,Motero usatsatire zochita za anthu osakhulupirira
  68,9,Iwo afuna utagwirizana nawo kuti nawonso agwirizane nawe
  68,10,Ndipo usamvere zonena za munthu wotukwana amene alibe phindu
  68,11,"Woononga mbiri ya anzake ponena Al Qalam\t613 za bodza"
  68,12,"Woletsa ntchito zachilungamo, wophwanya malamulo ndi wochita zoipa"
  68,13,woipa mtima ndipo wobadwa mosalongosoka
  68,14,Chifukwa iye ali ndi chuma ndi ana
  68,15,"Pamene chivumbulutso chathu chilakatulidwa kwa iye, amati: “Ndi nkhani za anthu a makedzana.”"
  68,16,Ife tidzaika chizindikiro pa mphuno pake
  68,17,"Ndithudi Ife tidawayesa iwo monga momwe tidawayesera eni ake a munda, amene adalumbira kuti adzakolola mbewu zawo m’mawa mwake"
  68,18,"Osaonjezera mawu oti: “Ngati Mulungu alola.”"
  68,19,Kotero kudadutsa china chake chochokera kwa Ambuye wako nthawi ya usiku ndi kuwotcha pamene iwo anali kugona
  68,20,"Ndipo m’mawa, munda udasanduka wakuda monga mdima wa usiku"
  68,21,Ndipo mmawa iwo adaitanizana wina ndi mnzake
  68,22,"Nati: “Mulawirire ku munda ngati mufuna kukakolola.”"
  68,23,"Ndipo iwo adapita, namanong’onezana wina ndi mnzake"
  68,24,“Palibe munthu wosauka amene adzaloledwa kulowa m’mundamo kudzapempha”
  68,25,"Ndipo m’mawa, onse adapita ndi mphamvu zotchinjirizira anthu osauka"
  68,26,"Koma pamene iwo adaona zimene zidachitika, onse adati: “Ndithudi ife talakwa.”"
  68,27,“Iai! Ndithudi ife tapwetekeka.”
  68,28,"wangwiro amene anali pakati pawo adati: “Kodi ine sindidakuuzeni kuti bwanji inu simunena kuti: Ngati Mulungu alola?”"
  68,29,“Iwo adati ulemerero ukhale kwa Ambuye wathu! Ndithudi ife ndife olakwa.”
  68,30,Ndipo iwo adayamba kudzudzulana kuti wina adali wolakwa
  68,31,"Iwo adati: “Tsoka kwa ife! Ndithudi Ife tidali ophwanya malamulo.”"
  68,32,“Mwina kuti Ambuye wathu adzatipatsa munda wina wabwino m’malo mwa uwu. Ndithudi ndi kwa Iye kumene timapempha modzichepetsa.”
  68,33,"Chimenechi ndicho chilango koma ndithudi chilango cha m’moyo umene uli nkudza ndi chowawa kwambiri, iwo akadadziwa"
  68,34,Ndithudi anthu onse angwiro adzalandira minda ya madalitso imene ili ndi Ambuye wawo
  68,35,Kodi Ife tidzasamala anthu angwiro chimodzimodzi ndi anthu ochimwa
  68,36,Kodi mwatani? Kodi inu mumaweruza bwanji
  68,37,Kapena kodi muli ndi Buku limene mumawerengamo
  68,38,Kuti inu mudzapeza m’menemo chilichonse chimene mukufuna
  68,39,"Kapena inu mwalandira kuchokera kwa Ife, lonjezo lotsimikizika mpaka pa tsiku louka kwa akufa kuti, ndithudi, inu mudzapeza zimene mukufuna"
  68,40,Tawafunsa ngati wina wa iwo angachitire umboni za lonjezolo
  68,41,"Kapena, kodi iwo ali ndi milungu ina? Aleke abweretse milungu yawo ngati iwo anena zoona"
  68,42,"Ndipatsikulimenechinthuchoopsachidzachitika, iwo adzaitanidwa kuti apembedze, koma adzalephera kutero"
  68,43,Maso awo adzayang’ana pansi ndipo adzanyozedwa kwambiri chifukwa iwo adauzidwa kupembedza pamene adali pa mtendere
  68,44,Kotero ndisiyire aliyense amene akutsutsana ndi chenjezo ili. Ife tidzawalanga pang’onopang’ono m’njira imene iwo saizindikira
  68,45,Ndipo Ine ndidzalekerera pa kanthawi! Ndithudi chikonzero changa ndi champhamvu
  68,46,Kapena kodi iwe uli kuwafunsa malipiro moti iwo ali ndi ngongole yambiri
  68,47,Kapena kodi iwo amadziwa za Buku lobisika kuti iwo akhoza kulemba
  68,48,Motero pirira podikilira chiweruzo cha Ambuye wako ndipo usakhale ngati amene adamezedwa ndi nsomba pamene adalira kupempha chithandizo iye ali m’mavuto
  68,49,"Ngati Ambuye wake akadapanda kumuonetsa chisomo chake, ndithudi iye akadakhalabe koma iye adaponyedwa pa mtunda pamene anali wolakwa"
  68,50,Koma Ambuye wake adamusankha ndipo adamuchititsa kukhala wabwino
  68,51,"Ndipo, ndithudi, iwo onse osakhulupirira akadakusokeretsa ndi maso awo pamene amakumbutsidwa ndipo amati: “Ndithudi uyu ndi Wamisala.”"
  68,52,Koma ichi si china koma chikumbutso kwa zolengedwa zonse